[Student "S"]
{NOTE: There is a better way to bid this hand using special conventions.

EAST has 17 points, but with a 5-card Major opens 1\S rather than 1NT. 
WEST isn't quite strong enough for a jump raise, so she bids 2\S. 
EAST has enough extra to make a try for game, so she invites with 3\S. 
WEST has enough extra to accept the invitation, bids 4\S.}

